Blender

ctrl-s: snap
tab: edit mode
s: scale
g: translate
e: extrude
i: set keyframe
shft-ctrl-z: constrain movement to x-y plane
shft-d: duplicate object

add subdivision surface modifier
ctrl-r: loop cut and slide (mesh tools)
mark sharp edges (object menu in edit mode)


ctrl-h
hook to new object


